## Visits chart (VX)

**Visits chart (VX)** displays a bar chart of Views, Unique Views for stats related to Current User, Current post and Sitewide.

![](data:image/png;base64,)

## Example usages

As part of the [directory demo](https://wordpress-868296-4436932.cloudwaysapps.com/), we created a dashboard page named “Analytics”. On this page, the logged in user can view combined stats related to their account and posts. On this page, we added **Visits chart (VX)** widget with mode set to Current User

![](data:image/png;base64,)

The same widget is used on the individual post stats page in **WP Admin ➝ Design ➝ General ➝** **Other ➝ Post statistics**, and in this case the mode is set to Current post

![](data:image/png;base64,)

To learn more about setting up analytics on your site, [check article](docs.getvoxel.io_articles_traffic-analytics_.md)
